# Privacy Policy for Snake Arcade

Last updated: [Add Date]

## Overview

Snake Arcade is a Chrome extension that provides a modern version of the classic snake game for quick and accessible gameplay within the browser. Your privacy is important, and this extension is designed to operate without collecting or transmitting any personal data.

## Data Collection

Snake Arcade does not collect, store, or share any personally identifiable information. This includes, but is not limited to:

- Name, email address, or contact details  
- Location data  
- Browsing history  
- Authentication information  
- Financial or payment information  
- Personal communications  

## Local Storage Usage

The extension may use your browser’s local storage to save game-related data such as:

- High scores  
- Game settings (such as speed, themes, or configurations)  
- Progress related to gameplay or challenges  

This data is stored entirely on your device and is not transmitted to any external servers.

## Data Sharing

Snake Arcade does not sell, trade, or transfer any user data to third parties. Since no personal data is collected, no data is shared.

## Remote Code

This extension does not use remote code. All scripts and assets are packaged within the extension and run locally in your browser.

## Third-Party Services

Snake Arcade does not use any third-party analytics, tracking tools, or external services.

## Security

Since no personal or sensitive data is collected or transmitted, there is minimal risk related to data exposure. All functionality runs locally within your browser environment.

## Changes to This Policy

This privacy policy may be updated in the future if the extension’s functionality changes. Any updates will be reflected by revising the "Last updated" date at the top of this document.

## Contact

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact the developer through the Chrome Web Store listing or the associated GitHub repository.
